# Encrypted secrets live in this directory.
# All *.yaml files are in .gitignore EXCEPT *.enc.yaml (SOPS-encrypted).
# To create or edit a secret:
#
#   sops infra/secrets/postgres.enc.yaml
#
# SOPS will open your $EDITOR. Write plain YAML, save, SOPS encrypts on exit.
# The resulting *.enc.yaml file is safe to commit — values are ciphertext.
#
# Required secrets for the register stack:
#
#   postgres.enc.yaml      — keys: postgres-password, keycloak-db-password
#   keycloak.enc.yaml      — keys: admin-password
